          <li><label><input type="checkbox" data-stage="stepup"> Track Dylan’s Saturday visits, Saturday overnights, and weekend progression separately.</label></li>
          <li><label><input type="checkbox" data-stage="proof"> Preserve proof of every completed, missed, refused, cancelled, or made-up visit.</label></li>
